🌐 Portfolio Website

A personal portfolio website built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to showcase my skills, projects, and contact information in a clean and responsive design.

📁 Project Structure
Portfolio-Website/
│
├── assets/        # Images, icons, and media files
├── css/           # Stylesheets
├── js/            # JavaScript files
├── CNAME          # Custom domain configuration (GitHub Pages)
└── index.html     # Main landing page

🚀 Features
Fully responsive design (mobile + desktop friendly)
Smooth navigation and scrolling experience
Clean and modern UI layout
Dedicated sections for:
About Me
Skills
Projects
Contact
Lightweight and fast loading
Deployed using GitHub Pages (if applicable)
🛠️ Built With
HTML5
CSS3
JavaScript (Vanilla JS)
GitHub Pages (for deployment)

